<div class="container">
    <!-- Earn Points -->
    <h2>How do I earn points?</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Click on 'Home' or on your name located in the top left corner.</li>
        <li>Choose a company from the companies list.</li>
        <li>Choose the product you want to publish.</li>
        <li>Read and accept 'Terms of Use'.</li>
        <li>Click on the 'Post' button.</li>
        <li>Earn points ;)</li>
    </ol>

    <!-- Use points -->
    <h2>How do I use the points I have already earned?</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Go to the company store.</li>
        <li>Click on 'Earns' located on the top panel.</li>
        <li>Choose a product from the list of products you have published.</li>
        <li>Click 'use'.</li>
        <li>Show the code to the cashier.</li>
    </ol>
</div>
